msgid "13300:[name]梨深[line]「そりゃ、男の子っていくつになってもそういうオモチャが大好きなんだなーってのは、なんとなく分かるけど」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]梨深[line]I mean, I know that boys like their toys, no matter how old they get.[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]梨深[line]「さすがにそんな大きなオモチャ、ひとりで部屋で振り回してるのは、どうかと思うよー」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]梨深[line]But I think you're a little too old to be swinging a big sword around by yourself in your room.[%p]"

msgid "13500:[name]梨深[line]「それが許されるのは小学生までじゃない？」[%p]"
msgstr "13500:[name]梨深[line]I think the oldest you can be and still do that is elementary school.[%p]"

msgid "13600:[name]梨深[line]「あ、でもでも、タクの個人的な趣味をあたしの前で披露してくれたってのは、ちょっと嬉しいかも」[%p]"
msgstr "13600:[name]梨深[line]Oh, but I'm kind of happy that you let me see your private little hobby.[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]梨深[line]「あたしにだけ秘密を教えてくれたみたいで。あはは」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]梨深[line]It's like you've got a secret that only I know! Ahahah.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "13900:な、なんだそれ。[linebreak]はあ、ビビって損した……。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:W-What? I felt silly for being scared.[%p]"

msgid "14000:部屋の隅に立て掛けておいたオモチャのディソードを手に取る。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:I went and picked up the toy Di-Sword in the corner of the room.[%p]"

msgid "14100:部屋の真ん中に立ち、それをエンスーキャラの見よう見まねで正眼に構えた。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:I stood in the middle of the room and held it out in front of me, in the best approximation of an ESO character that I could do.[%p]"

msgid "14200:よし、頭の中に剣のイメージを――[%p]"
msgstr "14200:Okay, time to envision a sword.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]梨深[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]梨深[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14400:梨深が、こっちを見ていた。[linebreak]目が合った。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:Rimi was looking at me. Our eyes met.[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]梨深[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]梨深[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]梨深[line]「ふ〜ん……」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]梨深[line]Hmm...[%p]"

msgid "14700:なんか、ニヤニヤしてる……。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:She was grinning.[%p]"

msgid "14800:僕は自分の顔が火照ってくるのを感じた。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:I could feel my face getting warm.[%p]"

msgid "14900:ついいつもの癖で、この部屋に自分ひとりしかいないつもりで剣を構えちゃったけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:I'd picked up the sword and posed with it, forgetting that there was someone else in the room with me.[%p]"

msgid "15000:きっと梨深の目には、今の僕がかなり痛々しく映っている……かも……。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:In Rimi's eyes, I must look like a total weirdo... maybe.[%p]"

msgid "15100:鬱だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:Crap...[%p]"

msgid "15200:自重して、剣を下ろした。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I put down the sword.[%p]"

msgid "15300:恥ずかしくて、梨深の方を見られない。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:I was too embarrassed to look at her.[%p]"

msgid "15400:穴があったら入りたいとは、まさにこのことだよ。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:I wanted to be anywhere in the world but where I was standing right now.[%p]"

msgid "15500:見なかったことにしてもらえないかな。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:Or maybe I could just get her to pretend she'd never seen it?[%p]"

msgid "15600:そうしてくれるなら土下座でもなんでもするね……。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:I was willing to beg if I had to.[%p]"

msgid "15700:そんな僕に、梨深が追い討ちをかけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:But Rimi decided just to make things worse.[%p]"

msgid "15800:[name]梨深[line]「ねえねえ、チャンバラごっこ？」[%p]"
msgstr "15800:[name]梨深[line]Hey, hey. Are you pretending to fight?[%p]"

msgid "15900:僕は首を横に振った。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I shook my head.[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]梨深[line]「いつもそういうことしてるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]梨深[line]Do you always do that?[%p]"

msgid "16100:もう一度、僕は首を横に振った。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Again, I shook my head.[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]梨深[line]「今日が初めて？」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]梨深[line]Today's your first time?[%p]"

msgid "16300:今度はコクコクとうなずく。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:I nodded fiercely.[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]梨深[line]「チャンバラごっこの相手役、あたしがしようか？\u3000よく分からないけど」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]梨深[line]You want me to be your pretend opponent? I mean, I guess I can.[%p]"

msgid "16500:僕は激しく首を横に振った。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:I shook my head back and forth violently.[%p]"

msgid "16600:っていうかチャンバラごっこじゃないって言ってるのに……。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I just told her it wasn't pretend fighting.[%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]梨深[line]「ねえタク。どうしてこっち見てくれないのかなー？」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]梨深[line]Hey, Taku. Why won't you look at me?[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16900:そんなの恥ずかしいからに決まってるじゃないかっ。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:Because I'm embarrassed, obviously.[%p]"

msgid "17000:まずいものを見られた。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:She'd seen something I really didn't want her to see.[%p]"

msgid "17100:隠していたエロ本を恋人に発見させられたときの男の心理状態は、きっと今の僕と近いに違いない……。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:This must be what it felt like when a girlfriend found her boyfriend's porn.[%p]"

msgid "17200:[name]梨深[line]「タクってさ……」[%p]"
msgstr "17200:[name]梨深[line]Taku, you're...[%p]"

msgid "17300:もしかして軽蔑されちゃっただろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:Was she disgusted by me?[%p]"

msgid "17400:最悪だ。なんとかして誤解を解かなきゃ――[%p]"
msgstr "17400:This was the worst. I had to find some way to help her realize it was a misunderstanding.[%p]"

msgid "17500:[name]梨深[line]「かわいいねー♪」[%p]"
msgstr "17500:[name]梨深[line]...pretty cute, aren't you?[%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]拓巳[line]「……え？」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]梨深[line]「かなりキュンと来ちゃったなぁ、今のは。あはは」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]梨深[line]That was pretty cute! Ahahah.[%p]"

msgid "17800:ＰＣデスク用のイスに置いてあった星来たん抱き枕を胸にギュッと抱きしめて、梨深は身もだえている。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:She'd picked up the Seira-tan body pillow that was next to my computer chair and was hugging it tightly.[%p]"

msgid "17900:バカにされてるのかと思ったけど、その態度を見る限り、どうやら本気で言ってるらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:I thought she was making fun of me, but from the way she was acting, she was serious.[%p]"

msgid "18000:つまり、梨深は僕に対して――[linebreak]不覚にも萌えた、と。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:Did that mean that Rimi had... found me “moe” for a second?[%p]"

msgid "18100:ホッとした。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:I was relieved.[%p]"

msgid "18200:嫌われたわけじゃなかったんだ。よかった……。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:She hadn't started hating me. Good.[%p]"

msgid "18300:[name]梨深[line]「そもそもそれ、どこで買ってきたの？\u3000高かったんじゃない？」[%p]"
msgstr "18300:[name]梨深[line]Where'd you even get that thing? It must've been expensive, right?[%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]拓巳[line]「い、一万円……。渋谷の……雑貨屋で……」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]拓巳[line]I-It was 10,000 yen... at a store in Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]梨深[line]「へえ、一万円か……安いのか高いのか、分からないけど。たはは」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]梨深[line]Huh, 10,000 yen... I'm not sure if that's expensive or cheap! Tahaha.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]梨深[line]「でもそんな大きなオモチャが、普通に売ってるんだね。あたし、そんな大きなのを直接見たのって初めて」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]梨深[line]But I guess they really do sell toys this big, huh? I'd never seen one so big in real life.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]梨深[line]「その雑貨屋さんに売ってるっていうのは、誰かに教えてもらったの？」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]梨深[line]Who told you about the place where you could find it?[%p]"

msgid "18800:やけに食いついてくるな……。[linebreak]こういう剣に興味があるのかな？[linebreak]こっそり梨深も中２病だとか。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:She was really interested in this. Was she interested in swords like these? Maybe she was secretly an otaku herself?[%p]"

msgid "18900:僕が剣を持っていることにはちょっとバカにしたような態度を取っておきながら、実は自分も欲しくてしょうがないってヤツ？[%p]"
msgstr "18900:She'd kind of made fun of me while I was holding it, but maybe she actually wanted one of her own?[%p]"

msgid "19000:それなんてツンデレｗｗｗふひひｗｗｗ[%p]"
msgstr "19000:Wow, that's totally tsundere, lol.[%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]拓巳[line]「じ、自分で、調べた……ネットで」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]拓巳[line]I-I found it myself... online.[%p]"

msgid "19200:[name]梨深[line]「ネットかあ」[%p]"
msgstr "19200:[name]梨深[line]Online, huh?[%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]梨深[line]「すごいな、なんでも情報が手に入るんだね。あたしは全然ダメ。パソコンなんてろくに使えないよー」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]梨深[line]Wow, you can find out about anything online, huh? I'm no good at that stuff. I have no idea how to use a computer.[%p]"

msgid "19400:[name]梨深[line]「で、その剣って流行ってるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "19400:[name]梨深[line]So, are these swords really popular right now?[%p]"

msgid "19500:[name]拓巳[line]「え……な、なんで……？」[%p]"
msgstr "19500:[name]拓巳[line]H-Huh? Why?[%p]"

msgid "19600:[name]梨深[line]「タクはどうしてそれを買おうと思ったのかな、って」[%p]"
msgstr "19600:[name]梨深[line]I was curious why you decided to buy it.[%p]"

msgid "19700:ホントのことを、梨深に話すべきかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:Should I tell her the truth?[%p]"

msgid "19800:これから一緒にいてもらうなら、今後本物のディソードを探すときに付き合ってもらうことになるかもしれないし、今ここで話しておいた方がいいかもしれない……。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:If she was going to stay with me, she might end up looking for the real Di-Sword with me, too. Maybe I should tell her.[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]拓巳[line]「こ、これは、ニセモノ……だけど……」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]拓巳[line]T-This one's a fake.[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]拓巳[line]「本物が……あるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]拓巳[line]But there's a real one, too.[%p]"

msgid "20100:[name]梨深[line]「本物？」[%p]"
msgstr "20100:[name]梨深[line]A real one?[%p]"

msgid "20200:梨深は怪訝な顔をして首を傾げた。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:Rimi seemed a little confused.[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]拓巳[line]「ほ、本物を、持ってる人を、ぼ、僕、知ってるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]拓巳[line]I know somebody who has one.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]拓巳[line]「２人、い、いる。同じ、学校……の、女子……」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]拓巳[line]Two people, actually. Girls... at our school.[%p]"

msgid "20500:[name]梨深[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "20500:[name]梨深[line]...[%p]"

msgid "20600:[name]梨深[line]「女子ねえ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20600:[name]梨深[line]Girls, huh?[%p]"

msgid "20700:[name]梨深[line]「女の子がこんなオモチャを欲しがるかな」[%p]"
msgstr "20700:[name]梨深[line]Would a girl really want to own a toy like this?[%p]"

msgid "20800:[name]拓巳[line]「ホ、ホント、なんだ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "20800:[name]拓巳[line]I-It's true![%p]"

msgid "20900:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、そ、それに、オモチャ、じゃない……！」[%p]"
msgstr "20900:[name]拓巳[line]A-And... they're not toys.[%p]"

msgid "21000:[name]梨深[line]「あ、ゴメン」[%p]"
msgstr "21000:[name]梨深[line]Oh, sorry.[%p]"

msgid "21100:[name]拓巳[line]「ほ、本物は、光るんだ……！\u3000それに、すごい、そ、存在感で……」[%p]"
msgstr "21100:[name]拓巳[line]The real ones light up. They look... really... powerful.[%p]"

msgid "21200:[name]拓巳[line]「僕……そ、それを、探してる……」[%p]"
msgstr "21200:[name]拓巳[line]I-I'm looking for one.[%p]"

msgid "21300:[name]拓巳[line]「それさえ、て、手に入れれば……僕は、す、救われるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "21300:[name]拓巳[line]If I can get one... I'll be saved.[%p]"

msgid "21400:[name]梨深[line]「救われる……って」[%p]"
msgstr "21400:[name]梨深[line]Saved?[%p]"

msgid "21500:梨深はポカンと呆けたような顔をしたけど、僕はいたって真面目だ。[%p]"
msgstr "21500:Rimi looked surprised by what I was saying, but I was totally serious.[%p]"

msgid "21600:それに、『将軍』に対抗するのにディソードは強い支えになる。[%p]"
msgstr "21600:Having a Di-Sword would give me a way to fight back against Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、それで、あの……て、てつ……」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]拓巳[line]So, um, I...[%p]"

msgid "21800:[name]梨深[line]「……？」[%p]"
msgstr "21800:[name]梨深[line]...?[%p]"

msgid "21900:一緒に探すのを手伝ってほしい、って言いたかった。[%p]"
msgstr "21900:I want you to help me find it, is what I wanted to say.[%p]"

msgid "22000:だけど、もし断られたらどうしようって考えたら、怖くて、不安で、なにも言えなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "22000:But the thought of her saying no made me so scared that I couldn't ask.[%p]"

msgid "22100:僕はニセモノの剣をその場に放り出し、ソファに座り込む。[%p]"
msgstr "22100:I threw the fake sword down on the ground and sat on the sofa.[%p]"

msgid "22200:ため息をつきながら、目を閉じた。[%p]"
msgstr "22200:Then I sighed, and closed my eyes.[%p]"

msgid "22300:梨深の方から、探すのを手伝ってあげるって言ってくれないかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "22300:Maybe Rimi would volunteer to help me find it?[%p]"

msgid "22400:そしたら、僕は即ＯＫするのに。[%p]"
msgstr "22400:That'd make things so much easier.[%p]"

msgid "22500:さすがにそこまで期待するのは無理があるか……。[%p]"
msgstr "22500:Maybe that was too much to hope for.[%p]"

msgid "22600:ただ、梨深は今までにも、まるで僕の心の声を聞いたかのように、ピンチのときに颯爽と現れてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "22600:But Rimi had appeared out of nowhere to help me before, when I needed her most.[%p]"

msgid "22700:だから、もしかしたら――[%p]"
msgstr "22700:So maybe...[%p]"

msgid "22800:[name]梨深[line]「とにかく。もし本物があったとしても、それこそ買ったりしちゃダメだよ？\u3000今タクが持ってるのはオモチャだからいいけど、本物ってことは銃刀法違反になっちゃうんだから！」[%p]"
msgstr "22800:[name]梨深[line]Anyway... even if there is a real one, you'd better not buy it, okay? What you've got now is a toy, so it's okay, but real swords are illegal![%p]"

msgid "22900:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "22900:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "23000:僕の期待はあっさり打ち砕かれた。[linebreak]うう、梨深にはがっかりだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "23000:My hopes were mercilessly dashed. Sob... Rimi, I'm disappointed in you.[%p]"

msgid "23100:まあ、梨深のリアクションは、きっと一般人としてはすごくまともなんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "23100:Well, her reaction was the one most people would have.[%p]"

msgid "23200:僕は、ここ数週間でいろいろと訳の分からないことに遭遇したこともあって、セナやあやせの話を信じかけているけど。[%p]"
msgstr "23200:The only reason I felt differently was because after all the weird things that had happened over the past few weeks, I believed what Sena and Ayase said.[%p]"

msgid "23300:……やっぱりディソードは、自分ひとりで探すしかない。[%p]"
msgstr "23300:I'd just have to find the Di-Sword myself.[%p]"

msgid "23400:[name]梨深[line]「それで、タク」[%p]"
msgstr "23400:[name]梨深[line]So, Taku...[%p]"

msgid "23500:梨深が、僕の横に座ってくるのを、気配で感じた。[%p]"
msgstr "23500:I could feel Rimi sitting down beside me.[%p]"

msgid "23600:[name]梨深[line]「その本物の剣を持ってる女子って……誰、かなぁ？」[%p]"
msgstr "23600:[name]梨深[line]These girls who have real swords... who are they?[%p]"

msgid "23700:声がすぐ近くから聞こえてくる。[linebreak]真横にいるぞ……。[%p]"
msgstr "23700:Her voice was coming right next to me. She was sitting right beside me![%p]"

msgid "23800:密閉した、薄暗い部屋で、ふたりきり。しかも、こんな隣り合って座っているなんて……。[%p]"
msgstr "23800:We were alone in a dark room, just the two of us. And she was sitting right next to me![%p]"

msgid "23900:緊急事態だ……！\u3000緊急事態発生！[%p]"
msgstr "23900:Emergency! We have an emergency here![%p]"

msgid "24000:[name]梨深[line]「タクに女子の知り合いがあたし以外にいたなんて……ちょっとビックリ」[%p]"
msgstr "24000:[name]梨深[line]I'm a little surprised that you know any girls other than me.[%p]"

msgid "24100:[name]梨深[line]「もしかして〜、カノジョ？」[%p]"
msgstr "24100:[name]梨深[line]Are they your girlfriends, maybe?[%p]"

msgid "24200:そ、そういう話題を、あえてするのか……。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:D-Did she have to ask that?[%p]"

msgid "24300:もしかして、梨深は僕を誘ってるのか？[%p]"
msgstr "24300:Was she trying to tempt me, maybe?[%p]"

msgid "24400:この話題から後に続く展開って、恋愛の話しかなさそうなんだけど……！[%p]"
msgstr "24400:Why was she talking about “girlfriends”?[%p]"

msgid "24500:それで告白っぽいセリフとか言われて、[linebreak]そのままいい雰囲気になって……とか……！？[%p]"
msgstr "24500:Was she, maybe, going to tell me she wanted to be my girlfriend? And then there'd be a romantic mood between us, and then...[%p]"

msgid "24600:む、無理だ、心の準備がまったくできてないよ！[%p]"
msgstr "24600:N-No! I wasn't ready for that![%p]"

msgid "24700:僕は目を開き、必死で首を振った。[%p]"
msgstr "24700:I opened my eyes and shook my head.[%p]"

msgid "24800:あやせもセナも……ミステリアスな存在だ。そしてどっちもデンパな不思議ちゃんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:Both Ayase and Sena were very... mysterious. Also, a little crazy, probably.[%p]"

msgid "24900:二次元キャラなら萌えただろうけど、三次元じゃ萌えない。"
msgstr "24900:If they were 2D characters, they'd be really moe. But not in 3D."

msgid "25000:[linebreak]特にセナなんて、話してるだけで怖い。[linebreak]普通に暴力を振るってきそう。[%p]"
msgstr "25000:[linebreak]Especially Sena! Just talking to her terrified me. She felt like she could beat me up at any moment.[%p]"

msgid "25100:二次元キャラなら萌えただろうけど、三次元じゃ萌えない。特にセナなんて、話してるだけで怖い。普通に暴力を振るってきそう。"
msgstr "25100:If they were 2D characters, they'd be really moe. But not in 3D. Especially Sena! Just talking to her terrified me. She felt like she could beat me up at any moment."

msgid "25200:できればあんまり関わり合いにはなりたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "25200:I didn't want to get involved with her at all if I could avoid it.[%p]"

msgid "25300:[name]梨深[line]「そっか。ちょっと……安心した、かな。たはは」[%p]"
msgstr "25300:[name]梨深[line]I see. That makes me feel a little... relieved, I guess. Tahaha.[%p]"

msgid "25400:[name]拓巳[line]「え……」[%p]"
